        "subject": "LU-1606 api: Package posix-wordsize.h for user space.",
        "message": "LU-1606 api: Package posix-wordsize.h for user space.\n\nInclude the libcfs/posix/posix-wordsize.h in the packaging\nfor user space, to appear as $(includedir)/libcfs/posix/posix-wordsize.h.\n\nlustre_user.h then includes posix-wordsize.h in user space only,\nwhich defines LPU64 and its other variants, which have crept into\nthe user space headers over time, making lustre_user.h unbuildable\nin user space on Linux.\n\nChange-Id: Ib2d6be2f141256a65efc61f50116325e7db654ca\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
